sentence_A: The present invention relates to a method for producing mattress by using latex. This involves mixing the latex of a typical factory with a chemical and then placing the latex in a foaming machine to cure to achieve the desired properties. The emulsion is formed into a gel and foam by the addition of the chemical sodium silicofluoride. These latexes are subjected to radio frequencies and heated to maintain the latex mattress product in its shape. Then the product is taken out from the mould,  the latex mattress is cleaned,  the moisture is removed,  and the product is dried to prepare the latex mattress product.
sentence_B: 用乳胶生产床垫的方法。这包括将一般工厂的乳胶与化学物质混合，然后将乳胶放入泡沫机中固化以获得所需的性能。通过加入化学物质硅氟化钠，使乳胶形成凝胶和泡沫。这些乳胶进入无线电频率，加热，使乳胶床垫产品保持其形状。然后将产品从模具中取出，将乳胶床垫清洗干净，除去水分，将产品烘干，制成乳胶床垫产品。

It is composed of a top sliding plate,  The sliding plate can slide by external thrust through the screw rod,  And the top of the central slide bar is inserted into a groove region through which the center penetrates,  the top of the groove is inserted into the groove region through which the center penetrates,  the top of the groove is inserted into the groove region through which the center penetrates,  and the top of the groove region is inserted into a groove region inserted into the groove region inserted into the groove region through which the center penetrates. And a lateral through groove region having an upper end of the lateral slide bar passing through and fixed to a bottom of the lateral slide plate. The other part of the side sliding rod is provided with a plurality of side liquid discharging pipes,  and one part of the flushing chamber is provided with a conveying valve. For receiving liquid from the rinse liquid supply portion and supplying the liquid to a bottom discharge pipe,  a top discharge pipe,  or a side discharge pipe with a through pipe. In another part of the cleaning chamber,  there is a control box in which there is a coin collector for controlling the operation of the motorcycle cleaner.
sentence_B: 自动摩托车清洗机由压力泵提供清洗液，压力泵将清洗液吸入摩托车清洗室，包括：冲洗室的底部是一个底部支撑板，该支撑板上安装有下部出液管，其顶部具有侧孔和中间孔，用于支撑顶部滑动单元的入口。它由一个顶部滑动板组成，该滑动板可以通过螺旋杆通过外部推力来滑动，并且在中心滑动杆的顶部插入中心贯穿的凹槽区域中，该凹槽的顶部插入中心贯穿的凹槽区域中，该凹槽的顶部插入中心贯穿的凹槽区域中，该凹槽区域的顶部插入中心贯穿的凹槽区域中插入的凹槽区域中插入的凹槽区域。并将其固定在顶部滑动板的底部。在中间滑动杆的另一部分上，安装有多个顶部出液管。以及侧向贯穿槽区域，其具有侧向滑动杆的上端穿过并固定到侧向滑动板的底部。而侧滑杆的另一部分则安装了若干侧向排液管，冲洗室的一部分则设置了输送阀。用于从冲洗液供应部分接收液体，并将液体供应到底部排放管、顶部排放管或带有通过管道的侧排放管。在清洗室的另一部分，有一个控制箱，其中有一个硬币收集器，用于控制摩托车清洗器的工作。

sentence_A: The utility model relates to a spring clamping type cantilever fatigue tester,  which is composed of a supporting unit,  a power starting unit,  a power transmission unit,  a clamping unit and a counterweight unit. The utility model is a testing machine for continuous reciprocating load (circulating load). Or fatigue of the material or equipment of the machine prior to use. The equipment components may be improved prior to manufacturing the machine. The fatigue testing machine is provided with a spring clamping device which can firmly clamp a sample without sliding in the testing process. The power transmission device adopts a universal groove type coupling. In order to solve the self-locking problem of the coupling,  the movement distance is increased. The utility model is suitable for material fatigue tests and commercial leads.
sentence_B: 弹簧夹持式悬臂疲劳试验机由支撑单元、动力启动单元、动力传递单元、夹持单元和配重单元组成。它是一种连续往复载荷(循环载荷)的试验机。或机器的材料或设备在使用前的疲劳。在制造机器之前，可以对设备部件进行改进。疲劳试验机具有弹簧夹持装置，在试验过程中牢固地夹持试样，不滑动。动力传递装置采用万向槽式联轴器。为了解决联轴器的自锁问题，增加了运动距离。适用于材料疲劳试验和商业引线。

sentence_A: The invention provides an opening/contributing valve that contributes to stable working characteristics. The valve housing has an inlet gate and an outlet gate. In addition,  the plunger is slidably mounted in the housing in the axial direction by external operation of the shaft,  and a pressure compensation device for compensating the pressure exerted on the plunger from the water at the water gate to the other side is generated. The plunger is installed on the base surface of the shell by sliding along one side of the axial direction to close the discharge between the water inlet door and the water outlet door,  and the plunger is separated from the base surface of the shell by sliding along the other side of the axial direction to make the discharge between the water inlet door and the water outlet door. The pressure compensation device includes a pressure compensation chamber generated on the other side of the plunger and a path for interconnecting one side of the plunger with the pressure compensation chamber.

sentence_A: The sugarcane chopping vehicle is developed for cutting fresh sugarcane,  only sugarcane stems are left,  and no sugarcane leaves and soil exist. And immediately loading it onto a truck to reduce the transport process and minimize damage to the sugarcane in the next year. The utility model is suitable for the size of the sugarcane planting area in Thai. The width of the sugarcane trough is 1-1.5 meters. The utility model adopts a power device as an engine,  is matched with a hydraulic system for use,  adopts a rubber wheel for moving,  and has the cutting efficiency of 17-20 tons per hour. It can reduce harvesting cost per mu,  and possesses strong maneuverability. Compared with existent cane harvester and foreign cane harvester,  it possesses greater advantage. The utility model is characterized in that the utility model is composed of a vehicle frame (1),  wherein,  the vehicle frame (1) is positioned in the center of the vehicle frame and is used for supporting various devices;  unnecessary stem tips of sugarcane fields which are more than 3 meters are cut by a cutting device (2),  and then,  sugarcane (3) is spirally pulled. The lodged sugarcane stems and leaves are separated,  and the lodged sugarcane stems and the lodged sugarcane leaves are separated by spiral screws. (4) cutting the sugarcane from the root of the sugarcane,  then separating the sandy soil from the sugarcane by a roller conveyor (5),  and then transferring the sandy soil to a sugarcane cutting unit (6) to cut the sugarcane into a size of about 1 foot. And a sugarcane leaf absorber fan (7) mounted on top of the cutting unit for generating absorber wind to absorb from the sugarcane leaves and from the sugarcane leaves,  and then the sugarcane conveyor bridge unit (8). The sugarcane is supported after cutting and transported to a laterally traveling sugarcane truck. The front wheel (9) bears the weight,  adjusts the front height,  and controls the left and right steering of the vehicle. And having rear wheels (10) carrying the vehicle and rotating to drive the vehicle forward and backward,  having control chambers (11) to effect visual cutting of the top and grooves;  ;  (Figure)
sentence_B: 甘蔗切碎车是为切割新鲜甘蔗而开发的，只剩下甘蔗茎，没有甘蔗叶和泥土。并立即将其装上卡车，以减少运输过程，并对次年的甘蔗造成最小的损坏。适合泰国甘蔗种植区的尺寸。甘蔗槽宽度1-1.5米。采用动力装置作为发动机，与液压系统配合使用，采用橡胶轮移动，切割效率为17-20吨/小时。它使每亩收割成本降低，且机动性强，与目前常用的甘蔗收割机和国外的甘蔗收割机相比具有较大的优势；其特点是由车架(1)组成，车架(1)位于车架的中央，用于支撑各种设备，通过切割装置(2)切割3米以上的甘蔗地不需要的茎尖，然后螺旋牵引甘蔗(3)。将倒伏的甘蔗茎和树叶分开，用螺旋螺杆将倒伏的甘蔗茎和树叶用螺旋螺杆将倒伏的甘蔗茎和树叶分开。(4)将甘蔗从甘蔗根部切下，然后滚筒输送机(5)将甘蔗中的沙土分离出来，然后将其转移到甘蔗切割单元(6)，将甘蔗切割成1英尺左右的大小。以及安装在切割单元顶部的甘蔗叶吸收器风扇(7)，用于产生吸收器风，以从甘蔗叶中吸收器和从甘蔗叶中吸收器，然后甘蔗输送桥单元(8)。在切割甘蔗后支撑甘蔗，并将甘蔗输送到侧向行驶的甘蔗卡车上。前轮(9)承重，调节前方高度，控制车辆左右转向。并且具有后轮(10)，该后轮(10)承载车辆并旋转以驱动车辆向前和向后移动，具有控制室(11)以实现对顶部和凹槽的视觉切割；；(图)

sentence_B: 窗或门隔板包括一个外部框架，该外部框架连接成一个矩形框架，该矩形框架具有一个内部空间，用于支持由至少一个滑动导轨组件组成的滑动面板组件的入口安装。包括后导轨和前导轨，其中连接部分的一端以可安装的方式安装。以及连接部的另一端将支架直接焊接到外框的内缘或将支架焊接到另一导轨组件上，外框的一侧设有传力基座。用于从外部向下端施加推力，下端压力线的一端安装以容纳与顶部部分为上压力肩的内压力基座叠加。为了承受传递的压力，顶肩可以上下移动到安装在后轨或前轨上的承压部件的下端。并且所述下压力支座的侧部具有以可容纳的方式固定所述压力支座的一端。并且所述压力支座的另一端直接焊接到所述外部框架的内边缘或通过所述底部支座以可接受的方式连接到所述外部框架的内边缘。

sentence_A: The utility model relates to a dust removing device for a fan,  which is an accessory of a rear cover of the fan. sentence_A: The utility model relates to a dust suction brush with a special structure,  which is provided with a plurality of holes or holes or holes. sentence_B: 一种具有特殊结构的吸尘刷，具有多个孔或孔或孔，刷毛位于刷的每个孔或孔的边缘，允许灰尘碎片通过该孔或孔。刷毛负责把灰尘拉上来，孔或孔负责把灰尘拉到梳子上，把灰尘拉到把手上，然后再拉到吸尘器上。由于这种特殊的结构，我们可以在需要的地方进行清洁，清洁时间短，但我们可以在更大的区域进行清洁，这样灰尘就不会散开。不影响或伤害使用者的呼吸系统。

sentence_A: The invention relates to a process for producing syrup by taking dry bananas as raw materials. The process comprises the following steps of :  extracting in series by adopting three enzymes,  namely pectinase,  cellulase and amylase,  wherein the concentration of the three enzymes is 0.05-0.15% of the weight of the bananas. The incubation temperature of the enzyme is 40-60 DEG C and lasts for 30-180 minutes. The banana is subjected to centrifugation,  separation or filtration,  diatom separation,  and evaporation with a distiller under pressure to obtain concentrated syrup.
sentence_B: 本发明涉及一种以干香蕉为原料生产糖浆的工艺，采用果胶酶、纤维素酶和淀粉酶三种酶，浓度为香蕉重量的0.05-0.15%，串联提取。该酶的孵育温度为40-60°C，持续30-180min。香蕉经离心、分离或过滤、硅藻分离，然后在压力下用蒸馏器蒸发，得到浓缩糖浆。

sentence_A: The liquid nitrogen temperature reducer according to the present invention uses a vacuum heater to reduce the liquid nitrogen vapor pressure in a cylindrical container having a sealing cover. The evaporation of the liquid nitrogen is increased,  heat is extracted from the liquid nitrogen,  and the temperature of the liquid nitrogen is reduced to a semi-solid state (the temperature is about-210 DEG C or less). The method of treatment of this condition is to pack the liquid nitrogen in a vacuum insulated container to prevent heat conduction,  convection and radiation. The operation of the machine is displayed by a pressure gauge and a thermometer. Operation of the machine is controlled by a power button.
sentence_B: 根据本发明的液氮温度降低器使用真空加热器来降低具有密封盖的圆柱形容器中的液氮蒸汽压力。增加液氮的蒸发，从液氮中提取热量，使液氮温度降低至半固态(温度约为-210°C或更低)。这种情况的治疗方法是将液氮包装在真空隔热容器中，防止热传导、对流和辐射。机器的操作由压力表和温度计显示。通过电源按钮控制机器的操作。

sentence_A: The utility model relates to an industrial dust remover for a ventilation filter of a storage tank,  which is provided with two main structural parts :  1. Air supply unit. 2. sentence_B: 用于储罐通风过滤器的工业除尘器有2个主要结构部分：1。送风单元。2。除尘器本体由金属制成，按制造工艺组装而成，包括折叠成形、折叠成形、金属模具成形。金属焊接。主体结构可以从底部用螺丝组装。机器是金属的。在安装过滤器的区域内形成一个圆筒。2型储罐通风过滤器工业除尘器的尺寸。滤芯长约380毫米，总高约950毫米，4个平板滤芯长约600毫米，总高约1700毫米。该装置的顶部是空气输送装置，它产生空气流量，从而产生原料粉尘的过滤过程。底部是过滤器，用于过滤原料粉尘和清洁过滤器。将压缩空气送入过滤器，使粉尘再次进入储罐。为提高除尘效率、输送原料、减少电能和减少安装除尘器的空间和麻烦，节省预算

sentence_A: The invention relates to a power generation system driven by gasification,  which comprises a gasification block (1),  a gasification gas purification block (2) and a power generation block (3). The gasification block (1) is structured and includes a gasification reactor (10) including a main body (11) structured by a gasification reaction chamber (111);  A first decompression structure (112) is generated on the top side of the body;  A second pressure relief structure (113) is arranged to partially surround the upper outer periphery of the body;  The gas deposition chamber and the dust deposition chamber (114) create an outer side surrounding the lower part of the body;  A fuel feeding mechanism (12) mounted on the upper part of the feeding mechanism and connected with the gasification reactor (10);  The in-furnace recording mechanism (13) is rotatably arranged at the bottom of the gasification reactor (10);  The first water tank (14) is fixedly mounted and rotated with the in-furnace recording mechanism (13);  And a gasification agent supply system (15) having a supply end connected to the furnace recording mechanism (13). The gas purification block (2) structurally comprises a primary gas purification block (21),  a secondary gas purification block (22),  a second water tank (23) including the entire lower part of the primary gas purification block (21) and the secondary gas purification block (22),  and at least one impurity fishing unit (24) is provided at the end and is used for fishing impurities in the second water tank (23). The power generation block (3) is structurally constructed and comprises a clean gas storage tower (30),  at least one internal combustion power generation engine (31) and a power distribution unit (32).
sentence_B: 本发明涉及一种由气化驱动的发电系统，包括气化块(1)，气化气体净化块(2)和发电块(3)。 该气化块(1)结构化地形成，包括 : 气化反应器(10)，包括 : 由气化反应腔(111)结构化地形成的主体(11)； 第一减压结构(112)产生于主体的顶侧； 第二卸压结构(113)设置成部分地包围主体的上外周； 所述气体沉积腔和灰尘沉积腔(114)产生包围所述主体下部的外侧； 燃料加料机构(12)，安装在所述加料机构的上部，并与所述气化反应器(10)连接； 炉内记录机构(13)可旋转地设置在气化反应器(10)的底部； 第一水箱(14)与炉内记录机构(13)固定安装并转动； 以及气化剂供给系统(15)，其具有连接到炉记录机构(13)的供给端。 气体净化块(2)在结构上包括一次气体净化块(21)，二次气体净化块(22)，包含一次气体净化块(21)和二次气体净化块(22)的整个下部的第二水箱(23)，至少一个杂质打捞单元(24)设置在末端并用于打捞第二水箱(23)中的杂质。 所述发电块(3)在结构上构成，其包括一个清洁的煤气储气塔(30)，至少一个内燃发电引擎(31)和一个配电单元(32)。

sentence_A: According to the present invention,  a roller type garbage collector is developed for improved efficiency,  and the plate rolls up the circumference of the bristles so that the bristles have a rebound force,  thereby increasing the shaking force on the powder. The box body is provided with a handle and is convenient to use. In addition,  the handle is compact in design and convenient to use in corners.
sentence_B: 根据本发明，滚轮式垃圾收集器是为了提高效率而开发的，该板将刷毛的圆周卷起，使其具有弹回力，从而增加了对粉末的抖动力。箱体有手柄，使用方便。此外，手柄设计紧凑，便于在角落使用。

sentence_A: The invention relates to a coffee roasting equipment with simple structure,  the production cost of which is lower than that of imported equipment,  but the quality of roasted grains is ensured. The coffee roasting device of the invention comprises a base,  a barbecue grill,  a casing,  a precursor,  a rear body,  a rotating bucket,  a feeding tank,  a pressure reducer,  a dust filter cylinder assembly,  a rotating cylinder driving system,  a dust exhaust cylinder driving system,  a dust exhaust cylinder assembly and the like five main components :  a precursor assembly,  a rear body assembly,  a rotating cylinder assembly,  a casing assembly and a dust filter cylinder assembly.
sentence_B: 本发明涉及一种结构简单的咖啡烘焙设备，其生产成本低于国外进口设备，但保证了烘焙后的谷物质量。 本发明的咖啡烘焙装置包括 : 底座，烧烤架，机壳，前体，后体，旋转斗，进料槽，减压器，滤尘筒组件，旋转筒驱动系统，排尘筒驱动系统，排尘筒组件等五个主要组件 : 前体组件，后体组件，旋转筒组件，机壳组件，滤尘筒组件。

sentence_A: The improved thermosetting and extruding process utilizes thermosetting heat energy to heat the thermosetting heat energy to the thermosetting wood between the thermosetting and wood. The heat energy flows through the passages between the heat pipes,  then the heat energy is transferred to the wood,  the moisture in the wood is vaporized to the outside by using the moisture as a medium,  and the moisture is sucked out through the air cleaner. When water is evaporated and absorbed,  the steam pipe valve is closed,  the fan valve is blown in,  and cold air is blown in instead of steam,  so that the temperature of wood is adjusted,  and the wood is kept cool before being used. Therefore,  the wood can not be burnt and bent. This is a time-saving and energy-saving method,  and can obtain high-quality wood compared with the conventional wood baking method.
sentence_B: 这种改进的热固化和挤压工艺是利用热固化的热能，在热固化和木材之间的中间，将热固化的热能加热到热固化的木材上。热能通过热管之间的通道流动，然后将热能传递到木材中，以水分为介质，将木材中的水分汽化到外部，并通过空气吸尘器将其吸出。当水分蒸发并吸干后，关闭蒸汽管阀，吹入风扇阀，将冷空气吹入，而不是蒸汽，以调节木材温度，使木材在使用前保持凉爽。因此，木材不会燃烧，也不会弯曲。这是一种节省时间和能源的方法，比过去的木材烘烤更能获得高质量的木材。

sentence_A: The dehumidifying oven utilizes the heat of the air conditioner to dehumidify the materials which need to be dehumidified under the specified pressure. In an internal pressure regulated oven,  low heat is utilized,  but good dehumidification is possible. The amount of cold obtained from the air conditioning system will be used to cool the air discharged from the oven,  thereby maintaining a stable operation of the air dryer. Compared with a heat source or a cold source,  the utility model utilizes less heat energy and higher efficiency to reduce the humidity of materials and can not pollute the environment. The utility model is a clean energy source and has no dust,  smoke or noise in work.
sentence_B: 除湿烘箱是在规定的压力下，利用空调的热量对需要除湿的物料进行除湿。在内部压力调节的烘房内，以利用不高的热量，但可以很好地除湿。从空调系统中获得的冷量将用于冷却从烤箱中排出的空气，从而保持空气干燥器的稳定运行。与热源或冷源相比，利用较少的热能和较高的效率来降低物料的湿度，不会对环境造成污染。它是一种清洁的能源，工作中没有灰尘、烟雾或噪音。

sentence_A: A fixed (Jun. 12,  57) air conditioning system (1) has air supply ducts (21,  22) disposed adjacent opposing walls (51,  52) of an operating facility (5),  and a cold air generator (11,  12) delivers cold air to sequential eyes of the air supply ducts (21,  22). A plurality of air supply openings (3) and a plurality of induction airflow generators (4) having air suction openings formed in the air supply pipes (21,  22) are respectively provided at positions opposite to the air supply openings (3). The cold air discharged from the cold air discharge chamber (3) is sucked out by spacing the suction chambers within a predetermined range from the cold air discharge chamber (3),  respectively,  to generate an induced air flow downwardly toward the opposite wall. The induction airflow generator (4) sucks a part of cold air discharged from the cold air releasing cavity (3) to generate an induction airflow. At the same time,  persistent cold air which is not absorbed by the induction airflow generator (4) diffuses in the vicinity of the cold air release passage (3).
sentence_B: 固定(57年6月12日)的空调系统(1)具有设置在操作设施(5)的相对壁(51，52)附近的送风管(21，22)，冷风发生器(11，12)将冷风输送到送风管(21，22)的顺序眼。在送风管(21，22)上形成的多个送风口(3)和多个具有吸气口的感应气流发生器(4)，分别设置在与送风口(3)相对位置上。通过在与冷风释放腔(3)的预定范围内分别间隔这样的吸入腔，它将从冷风释放腔(3)排出的冷风吸出，以产生向下流向对壁的感应气流。感应气流发生器(4)吸入从冷风释放腔(3)排出的一部分冷风，产生感应气流。同时，未被感应气流发生器(4)吸收的持久冷空气在冷风释放通道(3)的附近扩散。

sentence_A: A dust collector is a device for collecting dust samples from the environment for carrying dust to a laboratory for analysis. The utility model is realized by inserting the dust collector into the pipe end of the vacuum cleaner. The utility model is characterized in that the utility model is a cylindrical tube shape composed of end tubes which are contacted with a dust collecting area,  and a dust collecting chamber can filter and contain two layers of dust by a sieve plate and filter paper. And a front tube for insertion into the vacuum hose and tightly connected by internal locking threads.
sentence_B: 除尘器是一种用于从环境中收集灰尘样本的设备，用于将灰尘带到实验室中进行分析。它是通过将灰尘收集器插入真空吸尘器的管端来实现的。这种集尘装置的特点是由与集尘区接触的端部管组成的圆柱形管状，集尘室可以用筛板和滤纸过滤并容纳两层粉尘。以及用于插入真空软管的前管，通过内锁紧螺纹紧密连接。

sentence_A: A vehicle floor mat according to the present invention provides a dustproof mesh formed by crosswise weaving at least three fine synthetic fibers and one fine plastic wire. These ropes are woven into two webs. The gaps between the first and second webs are made into fine plastic threads. The two nets are vertically connected such that the first layer of net is raised from the second layer of net. According to the invention,  this is achieved in that the dust screen collapses when the feet are in contact and recovers when the feet are lifted from the carpet.
sentence_B: 根据本发明的车辆地垫提供了一种防尘网，该防尘网由至少三根细小的合成纤维和一根细小的塑料线交叉编织而成。这些绳子被编织成两层网。第一层和第二层网之间的缝隙被制成细小的塑料线。将两个网垂直连接起来，使第一层网从第二层网抬高。根据本发明，实现了这种做法，即当脚接触时，防尘网就会塌陷，当脚从地毯上抬起时，防尘网就会恢复。

sentence_A: A mobile door lock system for a vehicle with a centrally controlled lock system includes a mobile door lock mounted in the vehicle to receive signals from an individual or other mobile door lock. The user must have a 4-bit code to communicate with the unlocking system with the mobile phone. The 4-bit code is uniquely programmable and the 2-bit code is used for locking and unlocking.
sentence_B: 一种带有中控锁系统的车辆的移动门锁系统，该系统包括安装在车辆中的移动门锁，以接收来自个人或其他移动门锁的信号。用户必须有4位代码才能用手机与解锁系统通信。这4位代码是唯一可编程的，2位代码用于锁定和解锁。

sentence_A: According to a door lock device with a handle,  magnetic force from a magnet 2 fixed to a member on one side of a door frame and a member on one side of the door frame is applied by attracting magnetic poles to each other. The suction force is characterized in that the distance of the suction force is longer through the suction force instead of being stuck on the suction force,  so that the locking efficiency of the device is improved,  and the device for closing and opening is developed instead of a built-in handle.
sentence_B: 根据本发明的一种带有把手的门锁装置，通过将磁极相互吸引来施加来自固定在门框一侧的部件上和固定在门框一侧的部件上的磁体2的磁力。吸力的特点是通过吸力而不是粘在吸力上，使吸力的距离更长，从而提高了设备的锁定效率，并开发了用于关闭和打开的设备，而不是内置的手柄。

sentence_A: A brake and/or clutch and/or throttle locking device has the functions of locking brake and/or clutch and/or throttle locking and cutting off a starting lamp so as to prevent a vehicle from being stolen. The power system can be locked and cut off at the same time. The utility model is composed of a hinge steel plate. A steering column is fixed on the position of a clutch pin or a brake,  and a bolt is fixed on the position of the clutch pin or the brake. A steel plate with a through hole connects the broken bolt to the steel pipe and opens the other side. The utility model is connected with a key system by a steel pipe,  is connected with a steel plate on a padlock by a shaft,  and is connected with an electric bridge by a power-off switch. A smaller steel pipe can be inserted into a larger steel pipe and connected to a steel plate of a lock,  a clutch,  a brake or a throttle valve,  and is provided with a rubber iron core for a padlock. The utility model relates to a pull rope with a locking function. The other end can be processed into two pointed grooves.
sentence_B: 一种制动/或离合器/或油门锁止装置，具有锁止制动和/或离合器和/或油门锁止并切断启动灯的功能，以防止车辆被盗。动力系统可以同时锁紧和切断。它由铰链钢板组成，将转向柱固定在离合器销或制动器的位置，并将螺栓固定在离合器销或制动器的位置。有穿孔的钢板，将断螺栓连接到钢管上，打开另一边。用钢管连接到钥匙系统上，用轴连接到挂锁上的钢板上，用断电开关连接到电桥上。可将较小的钢管插入较大的钢管中，连接到锁、离合器、制动器或节气门的钢板上，并配有橡胶铁芯，用于挂锁。带锁紧的拉绳。另一端可加工成两个尖头的凹槽。

sentence_A: The utility model relates to an alarm device for remaining children in a student picking-up vehicle or an ordinary vehicle. The utility model is characterized in that a pressing pad is arranged in the vehicle to support the treading or the pressing treading of remaining children in the vehicle. For attaching the switch to the inside,  the tabs may be used to determine whether the switch contacts are connected,  connected,  or disconnected when the door is locked with a key lock or with a command signal. When the engine stops working,  an electrical signal wirelessly transmitted from the outside so that power supplied from the alarm device can be transmitted to a display lamp or speaker mounted on a student pick-up car or other vehicle.
sentence_B: 学生接送车或普通车辆中的残存儿童警报装置，其特征是安装在车内的压垫，以支持车内残存儿童的踩踏或压踏。用于使开关连接在内侧，压片可用于确定当用钥匙锁锁门或用命令信号锁门时，开关触点是连接、连接还是分离。当发动机停止工作时，从外部无线传输，以便从报警装置供电的电信号可以传输到安装在学生接送车或其他车辆上的显示灯或扬声器。

sentence_A: An accelerator locking device is disclosed. When the engine waits for air (vacuum) on the solenoid 1,  the throttle locking switch is pressed down,  the solenoid 1 is opened,  the air is sucked in through the air pipeline,  the vacuum piston is pulled,  and the throttle pipeline is slid. The throttle valve pipeline is connected to the vacuum piston. The solenoid switch 2 is pressed down. When the lock is released (the throttle valve is released),  the outside air enters the piston (the vacuum ball). The solenoid 3 is released. When the valve is released,  the outside air enters the piston (vacuum ball). When the brake current is turned on.
sentence_B: 油门锁定装置是公开的。当发动机在螺线管1上等待空气(真空)时，按下油门锁定开关，打开螺线管1，使空气通过空气管道吸入，拉动真空活塞，滑动油门管路。节气门管路连接在真空活塞上。按下螺线管开关2。松开锁(松开节气门)，让外部空气进入活塞(真空球)。松开螺线管3。松开阀门，让外部空气进入活塞(真空球)。当制动电流接通时。

sentence_A: The invention relates to a cleaning and pickling composition for cleaning photosensitizers used at the end of a production line,  This cleaning preparation does not contain amino acids,  Without water,  It is basically non-corrosive to copper and aluminum,  And contains at least one polar organic solvent,  At least one hydroxylated organic amine and at least one corrosion inhibitor compound having a hydroxyl functional group,  having the formula :  T1-[(Cr1R2) m (Cr3R4) n] p (Cr5R6) R1 and R2 is OH,  if one of R1 and R2 is OH,  it is selected from H,  alkyl or alkoxy,  m is an integer equal to or greater than 1,  R3 and R4 is selected from H,  alkyl or alkoxy,  n is 0 or a positive integer,  and p is an integer equal to or greater than 1;  At least one of R5 and R6 is OH,  and if one of R5 and R6 is not OH,  it is selecte from H,  alkyl or alkoxy,  and Q is an integer equal to 1 or more;  T1 and T2 were selected from group H,  alkyl,  hydroxyalkyl,  polyhydroxyalkyl,  Aminoalkyl,  Carbonylalkyl or amide or T1 and T2 may combine to produce a structure selecte from that group consisting of an aliphatic re structure or a condensed ring structure,  And any one or more hydroxyl-containing cosolvents,  corrosion inhibitor aryl compounds containing two or more OH,  OR6 and/or SO2R6R7 groups are directly bonded to the aromatic ring,  wherein R6,  R7 and R8 are respectively selected from alkyl and aryl groups,  metal complexing agents,  other metal corrosion inhibitors and surfactants.
sentence_B: 本发明涉及用于清洗生产线末端使用的光敏剂的清洗和酸洗组合物， 这种清洁制剂不含氨基酸， 没有水， 对铜和铝基本无腐蚀性，并且至少含有一种极性有机溶剂， 至少一种羟基化的有机胺， 以及至少一种具有羟基官能团的缓蚀剂化合物，其式为 : T1-[(Cr1R2)m(Cr3R4)n]p(Cr5R6)R1和R2中至少有一个为OH，若R1和R2中有一个为OH，则选自H，烷基或烷氧，m为整数等于1或大于，R3和R4选自H，烷基或烷氧，n为0或正整数，p为整数等于1或大于； 在R5和R6中至少有一个是OH，如果R5和R6中有一个不是OH，则从H，烷基或烷氧中选择，Q是等于1或更大的整数； 从H组中选取T1和T2， 烷基， 羟烷基， 聚羟基烷基， 氨基烷基， 羰基烷基或酰胺或T1和T2可结合产生选择自脂肪环结构或缩合环结构的结构， 以及任意一个或多个含羟基的共溶剂，含两个或两个以上OH，OR6和/或SO2R6R7基团的缓蚀剂芳基化合物直接键合在芳环上，其中R6，R7和R8分别选自烷基和芳基，金属络合剂，其它金属缓蚀剂和表面活性剂。

sentence_A: The invention relates to a method for recovering precious metals from waste electronic equipment at lower treatment cost. Waste electronic equipment is crushed by an impact crusher,  and these waste electronic equipment are separated into printed circuit substrate and non-printed circuit substrate raw materials. Then,  printed circuit substrates are ground by a rotary impact crusher,  and these substrates are separated into components and non-components mounted on the printed circuit substrate. Precious metals are regenerated from these separated parts.
sentence_B: 本发明涉及一种以较低的处理成本从废弃电子设备中回收贵金属的方法。 通过冲击式破碎机对废弃电子设备进行粉碎，这些废弃电子设备被分离为印刷电路基板和非印刷电路基板原料。 然后，通过旋转式冲击破碎机研磨印刷电路基板，这些基板被分离为安装在印刷电路基板上的部件和非部件。 贵金属是从这些分离的部件中再生出来的。

sentence_A: The invention provides an electronic article monitoring (EAS) mark screen detection system and method. The system comprises an electronic article monitoring subsystem,  a metal detection subsystem and an image analysis subsystem that communicate with a system controller. The EAS subsystem has the effect of detecting EAS tags in the detected area. The metal detection subsystem has the effect of detecting metal objects in the detection area. The image analysis subsystem has the effect of retaking the image of metal objects. The system controller has the function of determining the statistical classification of the metal object and calculating the confidence weight of the statistical classification. If the metal object is identified as an EAS flag screen according to this statistical classification and the corresponding confidence weight,  an alarm signal will be sent out.
sentence_B: 本发明提出了一种电子物品监测(EAS)标志屏检测系统和方法，该系统包括与系统控制器通信的电子物品监测子系统，金属检测子系统和图像分析子系统。 所述EAS子系统具有检测所述检测区域中的EAS标记的效果。 金属检测子系统具有检测检测区域内金属物体的效果。 图像分析子系统具有对金属物体图像进行重拍的效果。 系统控制器具有确定此金属对象的统计分类和计算此统计分类的置信度权重的作用。 如果这个金属物体根据这个统计分类和相应的置信权重被识别为EAS标志屏，那么就会发出报警信号。

sentence_A: The invention provides an X-ray analysis device,  which is used for irradiating a sample with an X-ray beam. The prepared X-ray tube has a source trace of the divergent X-ray beam generated by the X-ray tube having a characteristic first energy,  and the radiation energy is positive and negative;  The first X-ray optical part receives the diverging X-ray beam and directs the beam towards the pattern trace while generating monochromaticity to the beam;  And a second X-ray optical portion that receives the diverging X-ray beam and directs the beam towards the pattern trace while generating monochrome to second energy to the beam. The first X-ray optical portion may generate monochrome for characteristic energy from the source trace,  and the second X-ray optical portion may generate monochrome for braking radiation energy from the source trace. The X-ray optical portion may be a curved diffractive optical portion for receiving an X-ray beam diverging from the X-ray tube and converging the beam at the sample trace. Detection operations were also carried out to detect and measure various toxins in BAN artificial products including toys and electronic products.
sentence_B: 本发明提供了一种X射线分析装置，用于用X射线束照射样品，所制得的X射线管具有其所产生的发散X射线束的源迹具有特征第一能量，辐射能量为正负； 第一X射线光学部分接收发散的X射线光束，并将光束朝向图案迹，同时对光束产生单色性； 以及第二X射线光学部分，接收发散的X射线光束，并将该光束朝向图案迹，同时对该光束产生单色至第二能量。 第一X射线光学部分可为来自源迹的特征能量产生单色，第二X射线光学部分可为来自源迹的制动辐射能量产生单色。 所述X射线光学部分可以是弯曲衍射光学部分，用于接收从所述X射线管发散的X射线束，并使所述光束在所述样品迹处会聚。 还进行了检测操作，以检测和测量包括玩具和电子产品在内的BAN人造产品中的各种毒素。

sentence_A: The roller shutter door sheet is a component of the roller shutter door sheet,  and is characterized in that the roller shutter door sheet is rolled,  embossed and bent to form three roller shutter door sheets according to the length,  and the roller shutter door sheets are cut into roller shutter door sheets with certain lengths according to the purposes. The edge of the roller shutter door is rolled to a curved length for connection with adjacent roller shutter door members to form the roller shutter door. And on both sides of the end portion,  the roller shutter door locking lug members can be mounted.
sentence_B: 本发明所述的卷帘门片是卷帘门片的部件，其特征是卷帘门片轧制、压花、弯曲，按长度成形成三个卷帘门片，并按用途切割成一定长度的卷帘门片。卷帘门的边缘被卷绕成弯曲的长度，以便与相邻的卷帘门部件连接，形成卷帘门。并且在所述端部的两侧，可安装所述卷帘门锁耳部件。

sentence_A: An opening locking device comprises two parts,  wherein one part is fixed on one side of an opening or fixed on a frame of the opening,  and an ear protrudes out of the surface of the opening or the frame. A second portion is secured to the other opening,  wherein an end of the second portion has a cartridge having an opening for engaging the lock. The padlock is a U-shaped padlock,  and is characterized in that the padlock is consistent with a box body;  and the padlock is arranged in a way that when an opened door is closed and a lock rod of the padlock is pressed,  the lock rod of the padlock is aligned with a protruding lug of a first part. The end part of the lock rod is inserted into the hook ring,  so when the hook ring is in a locked state and the hook ring is hidden in the box body,  a thief can not cut the hook ring.
sentence_B: 一种开口锁紧装置，包括两部分，其中一部分固定在开口的一侧或固定在开口的框架上，耳朵突出在开口的表面或框架上。第二部分固定在另一开口上，其中所述第二部分的端部具有盒状物，所述盒状物具有用于嵌入所述锁的开口。其中，该挂锁为U形挂锁，其特征是与盒体一致，并且其设置方式是，当打开的门关闭并按压该挂锁的锁杆时，该挂锁的锁杆与第一部分的突出耳对齐。锁杆的端部被插入钩环中，所以当钩环处于锁定状态时，钩环隐藏在箱体内时，窃贼无法切割钩环。

sentence_A: The utility model is a box with at least three rooms. The first room is used for placing watches,  the second room is used for placing finished fish feed,  and the third room is used for assembling the spiral mechanism. The finished fish feed is rotated to an aquarium.
sentence_B: 本机是一个盒子，至少有三个房间。第一个房间是用来放手表的，第二个房间是用来放成品鱼饲料的，第三个房间是用来组装螺旋机构的。将成品鱼饲料旋转到水族馆。

sentence_A: The edited abstract 03/03/2016 automotive floor locking device (100,  200,  300,  400) includes side fasteners (101,  202,  302,  402) of at least one aperture (103,  203,  303,  403),  and side fasteners (102,  202,  302,  402) of at least one aperture (104,  204,  304,  404). A side mount (101,  201,  301,  401) having at least one aperture (103,  203,  303,  403),  a side mount (105,  205,  305,  405) having at least one aperture (104,  204,  304,  404),  and an inner mount (111,  211,  310,  410) and an outer mount (118,  218,  318),  418) characterized by an echo (116,  117,  315,  316),  a groove (106,  206),  a groove (107,  207,  306,  406),  a ridge (109,  209,  308,  408),  a welded portion of the ridge (110,  210,  309,  409).

The utility model relates to a lock body for locking a screen,  which is characterized by comprising a base part,  wherein each side part of the base part is provided with a supporting seat which is used for preventing the edge of a window frame fixed on the edge of the window frame or the edge of a door frame from falling off. And a lever protruding from the outside of the base portion for locking the shield door to the window frame or door frame. And a perforation in a central region of the base portion for guiding the cage nut to an edge of the window frame or door.
sentence_B: 一种用于锁屏的锁体，其特征在于包括底座部分，底座部分的每个侧部具有支撑座，用于防止固定在窗框边缘或门框边缘上的窗框边缘的脱落。以及具有从底座部分的外部突出的杆，用于将屏蔽门锁在窗框或门框上。以及在所述底座部分的中心区域，具有用于将所述锁紧螺母导向所述窗框或门的边缘的穿孔孔。

sentence_A: The outer sliding frame padlock of FIGS. 1-2 is used in conjunction with the inner sliding frame padlock of FIGS. 3-4. A shaft connected to the handle cover is pushed to the hooks of the two sliding frames,  and the spring is fixed to the two sliding frames. When the key is opened,  the inner core of the key is connected with the triangular compartment of the double sliding lock. When locking and unlocking are required,  the core will move the triangular compartment up and down. The second unlocking of the present invention as described in FIGS. 1-2 must be used with the present invention as in FIGS. 3-4 for outdoor sliding doors,  but is limited only to the present invention as in FIGS. 3-4. It is not necessary to assemble with the present invention in FIGS. 1-2;  For sliding windows.
sentence_B: 图1-2中的外部滑动框架挂锁与图3-4中的内部滑动框架挂锁配合使用。连接到手柄盖的轴将被推到2个滑动框架的钩上，并将弹簧固定在2个滑动框架上。当打开钥匙时，钥匙的内芯与双滑动锁的三角形隔间连接。当需要上锁和开锁时，该芯将使三角形隔间上下移动。如图1-2中的本发明所述的第2次解锁必须与如图3-4中的本发明一起使用，如图3-4中的本发明用于室外推拉门，但仅限于如图3-4中的本发明。不需要与图1-2中的本发明装配；用于滑动窗口。

sentence_A: Edited abstract 09/06/2011 automotive brake,  clutch or throttle locking device for triggering a mechanical design of a lock by twisting or rotating. The aim of the utility model is to improve the anti-theft performance. The utility model comprises a locking mechanism which can not be automatically locked when a vehicle runs or when a locking device is in a locking state. The utility model relates to a locking device for a brake,  a clutch or an accelerator of an automobile,  which designs a mechanical device which triggers locking by twisting or rotating. The purpose of the utility model is to improve the anti-theft performance. The utility model comprises a locking mechanical device which can prevent the locking mechanical device from automatically locking when a vehicle runs or the locking device is in a locking state.
sentence_B: 编辑摘要09/06/2015汽车制动、离合器或油门锁止装置，用于通过扭转或旋转来触发锁止的机械设计。其目的是提高防盗性能，包括提供一种锁止机构，使其在车辆行驶时或在锁止装置处于锁止状态时不会自行锁止。制动、离合器或汽车油门的锁止装置，设计了一种通过扭转或旋转来触发锁止的机械装置。其目的是提高防盗性能，包括提供一种锁止机械装置，防止在车辆行驶时或在锁止装置处于上锁状态时，锁止机械装置自行上锁。

sentence_A: A throttle lock device with an automobile seat pin includes a top bracket for supporting the insertion of a seat cushion nut or for supporting the insertion of a seat cushion floor,  and a side plate having a hole through a support plate. For supporting the engagement by an engagement plate connected to the base,  which is a rod or tube inserted or inserted into the top of the base,  and on the side connected to the base is an engagement plate having a hole through which the engagement plate passes. An engaging plate for attachment to the base,  and the other side of the base having an upper end of a connecting rod. sentence_A: The invention relates to a door lock (10),  comprising a lock box (11),  a key position (55) in the lock box that can be controlled to extend or retract,  a control lever (36) that can be controlled to rotate on one side of the door,  a locking device (28) that can be controlled to control a wrench on the other side of the door,  and a blocking device (81) that prevents the control lever from operating to retract the key position. In the closed and locked positions of the door,  the key position (55) protrudes,  and is opened by the wrench of the external locking device (28) by means of the blocking device (81),  so that the key position is fixed to the wrench of the blocking device (81). On the inside of the door there is also a key locking device (39,  40),  which is generated only for control and,  if necessary,  for deactivating the blocking device (81). The housing (38) fastened to the locking box has a second locking device (39,  40) which creates a guide groove (138d) for a spring-shaped connection (49) for connecting the operating lever (36) to the key position locking member,  and creates two key position locking members (69) sliding between them and a push spring head (66) surrounding the key position locking member thereon. The second locking device (39,  40) creates a guide groove (138d) for the rotating lever (41,  43) and the key position locking member (44) of the operating lever (36) for connecting the operating lever (36) to the key position locking member.

sentence_A: The utility model relates to a tunnel type mousetrap,  which is composed of a short and long mousetrap and a mousetrap,  wherein,  the front part of the tunnel type mousetrap is provided with a sliding door,  and the back part of the tunnel type mousetrap is provided with a bait cover. The mousetrap of the present invention has the following operating principle :  when the bait is placed on the hook and the door is opened,  the sliding latch will prevent the door from falling off. However,  when a mouse enters the cage and pulls the bait,  the force of the draw hook is generated,  so that the sliding pin opens the door leaf,  and the door leaf slides down and closes the inlet. When the mouse loosens the hook and tries to leave the cage,  the pulling force of the hook disappears,  and the sliding door bolt can lock the door again. sentence_B: 隧道式捕鼠器由短而长的捕鼠器和捕鼠器组成，前有滑动门，后有诱饵盖。有突出的钢制门闩，当有拉力时，悬挂在门闩的末端，使门闩滑动，打开门锁。门闩的特点是钢杆，横梁上有钢球。本发明的捕鼠器具有以下工作原理：当将诱饵放在钩上并将门打开时，滑动闩锁将防止门掉落。但当老鼠进入笼子并拉住诱饵时，就会产生拉钩的力，从而使滑动销打开门扇，使其滑下并关闭入口。当老鼠松开钩子试图离开笼子时，钩子的拉力就会消失，滑动门闩就会重新锁上门。滑动门闩的突出部分与门闩的上部相反，所以门不能向上移动。

The washing machine (100) having such a structure cannot be contacted by the water absorbing part (300) provided on the part of the rotary holder (116),  so that storage such as cleaning is difficult to be carried out,  and the effects of preventing mold diffusion,  dirt adhesion and detergent adhesion are achieved.
sentence_B: Sáng chế đề cập đến máy giặt (100) được bố trí thùng nước (108);  lồng quay (116) được bố trí quay được trong thùng nước (108);  và phần hút nước (300) được bố trí ở lồng quay (216). Máy giặt (100) có cấu trúc như thế đạt được hiệu quả ngăn chặn lan truyền nấm mốc,  ngăn chặn chất bẩn bám vào,  và ngăn chặn chất tẩy bám vào nhờ phần hút nước (300) được bố trí trên các phần của lồng quay (116) không với tay tới được và do đó,  khó thực hiện việc bảo quản như làm sạch.

sentence_A: The invention provides a washing machine,  which can electrically detect abnormal noise or machine failure caused by weight imbalance caused by washing object imbalance,  wherein abnormal swing caused by vertical swing is detected by first and second detection devices. The first detection device judges whether there is an imbalance between the water washing and the juicer cage by comparing numerical values,  judges from the difference between the rotational speed of the motor and the rotational speed obtained at a predetermined time interval by rotating at a low speed,  and determines a certain threshold value. The second detection means judges whether there is an imbalance in the water washing and water squeezing cages by comparing the difference between the reduction of the utilization coefficient maintaining a higher target speed relative to the low speed rotation and the reduction of the standard utilization coefficient,  and the threshold value. Abnormal swing caused by horizontal swing occurring during high-speed rotation is detected by the third detection device. This third detection device changes the threshold value from the reference utilization coefficient by referring to the degree of change of the utilization coefficient during high-speed rotation,  and then controls the motor to stop.
sentence_B: Sáng chế đề xuất máy giặt mà có thể phát hiện bằng điện sự mất cân bằng về trọng lượng do sự mất cân bằng của đồ giặt gây ra tiếng ồn bất thường hoặc hỏng máy,  trong đó,  sự rung lắc bất thường do sự rung lắc theo chiều dọc được phát hiện bởi phương tiện phát hiện thứ thứ nhất và thứ hai. Phương tiện phát hiện thứ nhất này xác định xem có sự mất cân bằng trong lồng giặt và vắt nước hay không nhờ so sánh trị số,  xác định được từ mức chênh lệch giữa các tốc độ quay thu được ở các khoảng thời gian định trước trong khi tốc độ quay của môtơ được gia tăng đến tốc độ đích cao hơn đối với quá trình quay ở tốc độ thấp,  và trị số ngưỡng nhất định. Phương tiện phát hiện thứ hai xác định xem có sự mất cân bằng trong lồng giặt và vắt nước hay không bằng cách so sánh mức chênh lệch giữa độ giảm của hệ số sử dụng mà ở đó tốc độ đích cao hơn đối với quá trình quay ở tốc độ thấp được duy trì và độ giảm của hệ số sử dụng chuẩn,  và trị số ngưỡng. Sự rung lắc bất thường do sự rung lắc theo phương nằm ngang xuất hiện khi quay ở tốc độ cao được phát hiện bởi phương tiện phát hiện thứ ba. Phương tiện phát hiện thứ ba này thay đổi trị số ngưỡng từ hệ số sử dụng tham chiếu bằng cách tham chiếu với mức thay đổi của hệ số sử dụng khi quay ở tốc độ cao,  và sau đó điều khiển môtơ dừng lại.

sentence_A: According to the present invention,  a vending machine for controlling the operation of a washing machine includes an electronic component for connection to a coin receiver and an electronic component for connection to various devices. Direct access to the washing machine without passing through the original control panel of the washing machine. The utility model can set the required coin quantity,  the washing program and the form of the water level measuring equipment. Once the coins have been inserted,  the circuitry commands the device. The utility model works in a washing machine from beginning to end.
sentence_B: เครื่องหยอดเหรียญสำหรับควบคุมการทำงาน ของเครื่องซักผ้า ตามการประดิษฐ์นี้ จะประกอบด้วยงจรอิเลคทรอนิคส์ เพื่อใช้เชื่อมกับตัวรับเหรียญ และเชื่อมเข้ากับอุปกรณ์ต่าง ๆ ในเครื่องซักผ้าโดยตรงโดยไม่ผ่านแผงควบคุมเดิมของเครื่องซักผ้า โดยสามารถตั้งค่าจำนวนเหรียญที่ต้องการ โปรแกรมการซัก ,  รูปแบบของอุปกรณ์วัดระดับน้ำ เมื่อหยอดเหรียญครบแล้ว วงจรจะสั่งให้อุปกรณ์ต่าง ๆ ในเครื่องซักผ้าทำงานตั้งแต่จนจบได้เอง

sentence_A: The invention relates to a washing machine,  which comprises an operating member that performs washing of laundry,  washing of laundry and extrusion of water of laundry;  The function decay time detection unit detects the time when the function decay occurs in the operation unit;  And a controller that gradually deteriorates the function of the operation member at a time when the function of the operation member is detected to deteriorate before the function of the operation member is stopped.
sentence_B: Sáng chế đề cập đến máy giặt bao gồm các bộ phận vận hành thực hiện việc giặt quần áo,  giũ quần áo,  và vắt nước cho quần áo;  bộ phát hiện thời gian suy giảm chức năng phát hiện thời gian xuất hiện sự suy giảm chức năng ở bộ phận vận hành;  và bộ điều khiển làm giảm dần chức năng của các bộ phận vận hành tại thời điểm phát hiện được sự suy giảm chức năng của bộ phận vận hành trước khi chức năng của bộ phận vận hành ngừng lại.

sentence_A: The invention relates to a test method for the tightness of the water-conducting details of an indicator for testing the tightness of the water-conducting details (11) in a housing (10),  which is mixed into or escapes from water when in contact with water droplets,  or is generated from a steam generator when in contact with water. According to the invention,  an indicator substance present in the form of a gas or vapor is detected by a sensor (13).
sentence_B: Sáng chế đề cập đến phương pháp thử độ kín của các chi tiết dẫn nước có sử dụng chất chỉ thị để thử nghiệm độ kín của các chi tiết dẫn nước (11) trong vỏ (10),  chất này được trộn vào trong nước hoặc thoát ra khi tiếp xúc với các giọt nước hoặc sinh ra từ chất sinh hơi khi tiếp xúc với nước. Theo sáng chế,  sự có mặt của chất chỉ thị ở dạng khí hoặc hơi được phát hiện bởi cảm biến (13).

sentence_A: The high-concentration ozone water deodorization system consists of a high-concentration ozone water production system (0.1-15 parts per million of high-concentration ozone water) pumped by a water pump. It enters the washing machine through the piping system of the washing machine when it reaches the last washing stage of the washing. When it reaches the last flushing stage of the washing,  it is controlled by the control cabinet. The control cabinet receives signals from the washing machine,  sends signals to the high-concentration ozone water generator,  and sends generated high-concentration ozone water to the washing machine through a pipeline system of the washing machine. When the high-concentration ozone water enters the washing machine and reaches the set water level of the washing machine,  the control cabinet sends a signal to the high-concentration ozone water generator to stop inputting the high-concentration ozone water. Then,  a time controller located in the control cabinet begins counting a predetermined time of at least 0.1 to 5 minutes,  which is a predetermined time at which the ozone water has a separate time to destroy the batt and the disinfectant fabric when the predetermined time on the time controller has been completed. The control cabinet can send out signals to the washing machine,  so that the washing machine can be taken out from the washing machine and then enters the next stage. The utility model has the advantages of good washable clothes quality,  uniform cleaning and no waste of time and cost. But also helps to protect the environment.
sentence_B: ระบบโอโซนความเข้มข้นสูงประกอบด้วยระบบผลิตน้ำโอโซนความเข้มข้นสูงปั๊ม มันเข้าไปในเครื่องซักผ้าผ่านระบบท่อของเครื่องซักผ้าเมื่อมันมาถึงขั้นตอนสุดท้ายของการล้าง เมื่อมันมาถึงขั้นตอนสุดท้ายของการล้างมันถูกควบคุมโดยตู้ควบคุม ตู้ควบคุมได้รับสัญญาณจากเครื่องซักผ้าและส่งสัญญาณไปยังเครื่องกำเนิดไฟฟ้าน้ำโอโซนความเข้มข้นสูงซึ่งจะถูกส่งไปยังเครื่องซักผ้าผ่านระบบท่อของเครื่องซักผ้า เมื่อความเข้มข้นสูงของน้ำโอโซนเข้าสู่เครื่องซักผ้าเพื่อตั้งค่าระดับน้ำเครื่องซักผ้าตู้ควบคุมสัญญาณความเข้มข้นสูงของโอโซนเครื่องกำเนิดไฟฟ้าและหยุดการป้อนข้อมูล จากนั้นตัวควบคุมเวลาที่ตั้งอยู่ในตู้ควบคุมจะเริ่มนับเวลาที่กําหนดไว้อย่างน้อย 0.1-5 นาทีซึ่งเป็นเวลาที่กําหนดไว้สําหรับน้ําโอโซนในตัวควบคุมเวลาที่เสร็จสมบูรณ์เมื่อมีเวลาอิสระท ตู้ควบคุมจะส่งสัญญาณไปยังเครื่องซักผ้าเพื่อให้เครื่องซักผ้าจะถูกลบออกจากเครื่องซักผ้าและย้ายไปยังขั้นตอนต่อไป สามารถซักผ้าที่มีคุณภาพสูงสะอาดและไม่เสียเวลาและค่าใช้จ่าย และยังช่วยปกป้องสิ่งแวดล้อม

sentence_A: The invention relates to a vacuum cleaner,  which comprises a fixed pole unit (24) having a pin pole (27) arranged in an exposed manner at an upper part of a connecting pipe (34) of a hose (21),  and a contact pole is arranged inside the vacuum cleaner main body and corresponds to the pin pole (27) of the fixed pole unit (24). Some of the contact poles are arranged horizontally when viewed from the interlocking dimensions of the connecting tube (34). The remaining contact poles are arranged obliquely relative to the horizontal position. This prevents loosening at the connection part of the hose (21) and the main body,  which may normally occur due to twisting of the hose (21) and the main body. According to this,  a vacuum cleaner with high reliability can be realized.
sentence_B: Sáng chế đề cập đến máy hút bụi bao gồm bộ phận cực cố định (24) có các cực chân cắm (27) được bố trí theo cách lộ ra ngoài ở phần trên của ống nối (34) của ống mềm (21),  và các cực tiếp xúc được bố trí ở bên trong thân chính của máy hút bụi,  tương ứng với các cực chân cắm (27) của bộ phận cực cố định (24). Một số cực tiếp xúc được bố trí theo chiều nằm ngang khi nhìn từ chiều lồng vào của ống nối (34). Các cực tiếp xúc còn lại được bố trí theo cách nghiêng so với vị trí nằm ngang. Điều này ngăn ngừa sự nới lỏng ở phần nối của ống mềm (21) và thân chính mà có thể xảy ra điển hình do việc xoắn ống mềm (21) và thân chính. Theo đó,  có thể đạt được máy hút bụi có độ tin cậy cao.

sentence_A: The invention relates to a washing machine,  comprising a controller (43) powered by a power supply unit;  A non-changeable memory (52);  A power-off switch (16) that disables power to the controller;  Wherein the controller stores a specific mode of operation and a process state of an ongoing operation in an immutable memory,  When the operation cycle normally ends or when the power interruption switch (16) has been controlled to interrupt the power supply to the controller (43),  The information stored in the non-changeable memory (52) is cancelled,  It is determined whether the information stored in the non-changeable memory (52) has been cancelled when the controller (43) is supplied with power,  and when it is determined that the information stored in the non-changeable memory (52) has not been cancelled,  the operation cycle is restarted from the state of the process and the specific operation mode stored in the non-changeable memory (52).
sentence_B: Sáng chế đề cập đến máy giặt bao gồm bộ điều khiển (43) được cấp điện bởi bộ cấp điện;  bộ nhớ bất khả biến (52);  một bộ chuyển mạch ngắt điện (16) mà ngắt việc cấp điện cho bộ điều khiển;  trong đó bộ điều khiển (43) lưu trữ các chế độ vận hành cụ thể và tình trạng tiến trình của hoạt động đang tiếp diễn trong bộ nhớ bất khả biến (52),  hủy thông tin lưu trữ trong bộ nhớ bất khả biến (52) khi chu trình hoạt động được kết thúc bình thường hoặc khi bộ chuyển mạch ngắt điện (16) đã được điều khiển để ngắt việc cấp điện cho bộ điều khiển (43),  xác định liệu thông tin lưu trữ trong bộ nhớ bất khả biến (52) đã được hủy hay chưa khi điện được cấp cho bộ điều khiển (43) và khởi động lại chu trình hoạt động từ tình trạng của tiến trình và các chế độ vận hành cụ thể được lưu trữ trong bộ nhớ bất khả biến (52) khi xác định rằng thông tin được lưu trữ trong bộ nhớ bất khả biến (52) chưa bị hủy.

sentence_A: The invention relates to a washing machine comprising a washing cage for washing,  Dry the laundry,  The lid opens and closes the doors and windows,  The unit detects the opening and closing of the lid,  A laundry detection unit for detecting the presence or absence of laundry in the laundry cage,  a laundry cage drying unit,  and a laundry detection unit for controlling the presence or absence of laundry in the laundry cage when the opening and closing of the lid are detected by the opening and closing detection unit of the lid after the laundry work is completed. The control unit also controls the washing cage drying unit so that when the washing cage detection unit indicates that there is no washing laundry in the washing cage,  the washing cage drying work is performed by the washing cage drying unit.
sentence_B: Sáng chế đề cập đến máy giặt bao gồm lồng giặt để giặt,  giũ và vắt khô đồ giặt,  nắp mở và đóng ô cửa,  bộ phận phát hiện việc mở và đóng nắp,  bộ phận phát hiện đồ giặt để phát hiện sự có mặt hoặc không có mặt của đồ giặt trong lồng giặt,  bộ phận sấy khô lồng giặt,  và thiết bị điều khiển để điều khiển bộ phận phát hiện đồ giặt sao cho sự có mặt hoặc không có mặt của đồ giặt trong lồng giặt được phát hiện bởi bộ phận phát hiện đồ giặt khi việc mở và đóng nắp được phát hiện bởi bộ phận phát hiện việc mở và đóng nắp sau khi công đoạn giặt đã được kết thúc. Thiết bị điều khiển còn điều khiển bộ phận sấy khô lồng giặt sao cho công đoạn sấy khô lồng giặt được thực hiện bởi bộ phận sấy khô lồng giặt khi bộ phận phát hiện đồ giặt cho biết rằng không có đồ giặt trong lồng giặt.

sentence_A: The invention relates to a washing machine,  which comprises a washing basin which is opened upwardly to accommodate washing clothes and washing water,  and a stirrer (7) arranged at the bottom of the washing basin,  which is rotated by a rotary drive unit. In addition,  the stirrer (7) includes a central wing (27) projecting from a rotation center (7a) of the stirrer (7) to a periphery (7b) of the stirrer (7),  a central wing (27) projecting from a base plate (26) of the stirrer (7),  a peripheral wing (28) projecting from the periphery (7b) to the rotation center (7a),  and a peripheral wing (28) projecting from the base plate (26) of the stirrer (7). In addition,  the center wing (27) and the peripheral wing (28) are provided at different positions in the circumferential direction of the stirrer unit (7). Thus,  the washing machine can be realized,  and thus,  even if the amount of washing water used is very small compared with the amount of washing,  non-uniformity during washing is unlikely to occur.
sentence_B: Sáng chế đề cập đến máy giặt bao gồm bồn giặt,  được mở hướng lên trên,  để chứa đồ giặt và nước giặt,  và bộ phận khuấy (7),  được bố trí ở phần đáy bên trong của bồn giặt,  được quay bởi bộ phận truyền động quay. Hơn nữa,  bộ phận khuấy (7) bao gồm các cánh trung tâm (27) kéo dài từ tâm quay (7a) của bộ phận khuấy (7) về phía ngoại biên (7b) của bộ phận khuấy (7),  các cánh trung tâm (27) được nhô lên từ đế (26) của bộ phận khuấy (7),  và các cánh ngoại biên (28) kéo dài từ ngoại biên (7b) về phía tâm quay (7a),  các cánh ngoại biên (28) được nhô lên từ đế (26) của bộ phận khuấy (7). Ngoài ra,  các cánh trung tâm (27) và các cánh ngoại biên (28) được bố trí ở các vị trí khác nhau theo hướng chu vi của bộ phận khuấy (7). Máy giặt do đó có thể được thực hiện,  theo đó sự không đồng đều khi giặt đồ giặt là khó xảy ra ngay cả trong trường hợp lượng nước giặt được sử dụng là nhỏ so với khối lượng đồ giặt.

sentence_A: The invention provides a fixing support structure of a portable visual perception electronic product. The invention comprises a mounting base and the visual perception of the guide groove on the back of the electronic product. Such a mounting base is slidable into the guide groove. And it is introduced into the portable visual perception electronic product. On the back of the portable visual perception electronic product. The utility model is a bracket with one end shaking the body,  and the electronic product on the back surface of the bracket can be visually perceived to be portable. The fixing support structure is used for firmly and reliably fixing the portable visual perception electronic products together,  and brings pleasure for users to watch programs. The product is not held in hand. Furthermore,  the user does not worry about the electronic product will fall from the hand,  this kind of fixed support structure can play a role in many respects. The utility model can be applied to various vehicles,  and can be used for fixing the portable visual perception electronic products used at present no matter running or parking. Thus,  the fixed support structure according to the present invention can be widely used in industrial and commercial fields.
sentence_B: การประดิษฐ์นี้จะเป็นโครงสร้างรองรับแบบยึดอยู่กับที่สำหรับผลิตภัณฑ์อิเล็กทรอนิกส์รับรู้ด้วยสายตาแบบพกพาได้ การประดิษฐ์นี้จะประกอบด้วยฐานยึดและร่องนำทางที่อยู่ด้านหลังของผลิตภัณฑ์อิเล็กทรอนิกส์รับรู้ด้วยสายตา ฐานยึดดังกล่าวจะถูกเลื่อนเข้าไปในร่องนำทางได้ และมันจะถูกนำเข้าไปเชื่อมต่อกับผลิตภัณฑ์อิเล็กทรอนิกส์รับรู้ด้วยสายตาแบบพกพาได้ ที่ด้านหลังของผลิตภัณฑ์อิเล็กทรอนิกส์รับรู้ด้วยสายตาแบบพกพาได้ดังกล่าว จะเป็นตัวรองรับที่มีปลายด้านหนึ่งโยกตัวกับทางด้านหลังของผลิตภัณฑ์อิเล็กทรอนิกส์รับรู้ด้วยสายตาแบบพกพาได้ โครงสร้างรองรับแบบยึดอยู่กับที่นี้จะถูกนำมาใช้ยึดผลิตภัณฑ์อิเล็กทรอนิกส์รับรู้ด้วยสายตาแบบพกพาได้อย่างมั่นคงและอย่างน่าเชื่อถือ ซึ่งจะทำให้ผู้ใช้ได้รับความสำราญในการรับชมโปรแกรมต่างๆ โดยไม่ต้องจับผลิตภัณฑ์ไว้ในมือ นอกจากนี้ผู้ใช้จะไม่มีความกังวลว่าผลิตภัณฑ์อิเล็กทรอนิกส์จะหลุดออกจากมือได้โครงสร้างรองรับแบบยึดอยู่กับที่นี้จะทำงานได้หลายทาง และมันจะถูกนำไปใช้งานกับรถยนต์ชนิดต่างๆได้ทั้งที่กำลังแล่นอยู่หรือจอดอญู่กับที่ การใช้งานในการยึดตรึงผลิตภัณฑ์อิเล็กทรอนิกส์รับรู้ด้วยสายตาแบบพกพาได้ที่ใช้กันอยู่ในปัจจุบันได้หมด จึงทำให้โครงสร้างรองรับแบบยึดอยู่กับที่ตามการประดิษฐ์นี้ถูกนำไปใช้ประโยชน์ในทางพณิชกรรมและอุตสาหกรรมได้อย่างกว้างขวาง

sentence_A: A vending machine with washing machine operating condition monitoring includes a receiving unit for receiving an input signal to indicate that the washing machine has received a power supply. A second relay transmission unit for switching the position of the start button of the washing machine;  A second receiving unit for receiving a signal when the washing machine has been started;  A third relay transmission unit;  A button position for switching water into the bucket is switched to a receiver unit III for receiving a signal indicating a predetermined level of water into the bucket. If the washing machine goes wrong in the processes of receiving a first receiving position,  a second receiving position and a third receiving position,  the processor will instruct the washing machine to return to work again,  which is the characteristic of repeated work. The washing machine does not eat coins,  but if a problem still exists,  the processor will send a signal to the receiving portion,  read the price of the coins,  and return the coins to the user.
sentence_B: เครื่องขายสินค้าอัตโนมัติที่มีการตรวจสอบสถานะการทำงานของเครื่องซักผ้ารวมถึงหน่วยรับสัญญาณที่ได้รับเพื่อบ่งชี้ว่าเครื่องซักผ้าได้รับพลังงาน รีเลย์ส่งหน่วยที่สองสำหรับการเปลี่ยนตำแหน่งของปุ่มเริ่มต้นเครื่องซักผ้า หน่วยรับสัญญาณที่ได้รับเมื่อเครื่องซักผ้าได้เริ่มขึ้นแล้ว รีเลย์ส่งหน่วยสาม ใช้เพื่อเปลี่ยนตำแหน่งของปุ่มน้ำเข้าไปในถังเพื่อรับสัญญาณที่บ่งชี้ว่าน้ำจะเข้าสู่ระดับที่ตั้งไว้ในถัง ในหมู่พวกเขาถ้าเครื่องซักผ้ามีปัญหาในการรับตำแหน่งรับสองตำแหน่งและได้รับสามได้รับตำแหน่งหน่วยประมวลผลจะสั่งให้มันกลับมาทำงานอีกครั้งซึ่งเป็นลักษณะของงานซ้ำ เครื่องซักผ้าไม่กินเหรียญแต่ถ้าปัญหายังคงมีอยู่หน่วยประมวลผลจะส่งสัญญาณไปยังส่วนที่ได้รับอ่านราคาเหรียญและคืนเหรียญให้กับผู้ใช้

sentence_A: The invention relates to a filter comprising a filter cloth (110) having a waveform,  a holding portion (120) located inside the filter cloth (110),  a bearing groove (112) created at each inner bend portion (111) folded to the longitudinal holding portion of the filter membrane,  and a toughening detail (113) inserted into the bearing groove (112).
sentence_B: Sáng chế đề cập đến bộ lọc bao gồm vải lọc (110) có dạng sóng,  phần giữ (120) nằm bên trong vải lọc (110),  rãnh mang (112) được tạo ra ở mỗi phần uốn bên trong (111) đã gấp nếp tỳ vào phần giữ theo phương dọc của màng lọc,  và chi tiết tăng bền (113) được đưa vào trong rãnh mang (112).

sentence_A: The invention relates to a composite multi-purpose washing machine,  which is improved on the basis of a casing,  a washing basin and a washing machine,  so that the technical conditions are the same in the casing. More specifically,  A clean machine,  Includes a frame disposed on the upper part of the housing,  The washing machine cover is connected with the machine frame through a rotary joint,  a control switch and a washing machine water inlet conduction joint are arranged on the machine frame,  the drum dryer is arranged at one side of the washing machine located in the machine case,  the corresponding front door of the drum dryer is arranged in front of the machine case,  and the washing machine basin is arranged at the side frame on the drum dryer. Compared with the current technical situation,  the invention creatively combines the washing machine,  the laundry basin and the laundry dryer together to form an integral whole according to the national safety standard. The invention has the following advantages,  including less occupied space,  low manufacturing price,  complete functions,  appropriate height,  convenient installation,  low noise and vibration,  low transportation price and unified universal modeling. In addition,  the composite multi-purpose cleaning machine also has the advantages of saving time and energy. This machine has flexibility and convenience in use and has product competitiveness in the market.
sentence_B: Sáng chế đề cập đến máy làm sạch đa năng phức hợp,  được cải tiến trên cơ sở vỏ máy,  chậu giặt và máy giặt để trong vỏ máy và giống với tình trạng kỹ thuật. Cụ thể hơn,  sáng chế đề cập đến máy làm sạch bao gồm khung được bố trí trên phần trên của vỏ máy,  nắp đậy máy giặt được nối bằng khớp xoay với khung,  công tắc điều khiển và đầu nối dẫn nước vào của máy giặt được lắp trên khung,  máy sấy quần áo dạng trống được đặt ở một phía của máy giặt nằm trong vỏ máy,  cửa mở ra phía trước tương ứng với máy sấy quần áo dạng trống được bố trí ở phía trước của vỏ máy,  và chậu giặt được đặt ở khung bên trên máy sấy quần áo dạng trống. So với tình trạng kỹ thuật,  máy giặt,  chậu giặt và máy sấy quần áo được kết hợp sáng tạo để tạo ra một bộ phận liền khối theo các tiêu chuẩn an toàn quốc gia,  sáng chế có các ưu điểm sau đây bao gồm chiếm ít không gian hơn,  giá thành sản xuất thấp,  đầy đủ chức năng,  chiều cao thích hợp,  lắp đặt tiện lợi,  độ ồn và độ rung thấp hơn,  giá thành vận chuyển thấp và kiểu dáng chung đồng nhất. Ngoài ra,  máy làm sạch đa năng phức hợp có ưu điểm là tiết kiệm thời gian và năng lượng sử dụng. Máy đem lại sự tính linh hoạt và tiện dụng khi sử dụng,  và có tính cạnh tranh về sản phẩm trên thị trường.

sentence_A: Portable mini-washer with casing, washing cup and transparent window on the outer frame. The outer frame defines the empty space inside.
